1
00:00:11,010 --> 00:00:13,350
I wish the mailpony
would just come already!

2
00:00:13,500 --> 00:00:17,250
I can't wait another minute to find out
if Rainbow Dash got in or not!

3
00:00:17,400 --> 00:00:20,650
Pinkie Pie, you're more nervous
than Rainbow Dash!

4
00:00:20,800 --> 00:00:22,600
I'm not nervous at all!

5
00:00:22,750 --> 00:00:24,650
When I get into
the Wonderbolt Academy--

6
00:00:24,800 --> 00:00:27,050
If you get in!
If you get in!

7
00:00:27,200 --> 00:00:28,300
Don't jinx it!

8
00:00:28,450 --> 00:00:30,660
I'm telling you,
it's in the bag!

9
00:00:30,810 --> 00:00:31,530
Don't jinx it!

10
00:00:31,680 --> 00:00:33,870
She is the best flyer in Ponyville.

11
00:00:34,020 --> 00:00:35,500
In Ponyville?

12
00:00:37,300 --> 00:00:40,410
I'm probably the best flyer
in all of Equestria.

13
00:00:40,560 --> 00:00:41,439
I wouldn't be surprised

14
00:00:41,590 --> 00:00:43,340
if they just went ahead,
and made me a Wonderbolt

15
00:00:43,490 --> 00:00:45,290
on the first day.

16
00:00:46,150 --> 00:00:47,660
Got a letter here
for Rainbow Dash.

17
00:00:52,060 --> 00:00:53,790
I... didn't get in.

18
00:00:56,430 --> 00:00:57,860
Gotcha!

19
00:00:59,820 --> 00:01:03,490
You guys are so gullible.
Like I wasn't gonna get in!

20
00:01:04,240 --> 00:01:08,500
I'm just sooooooooo
happy for you!

21
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:11,140
Uh... thanks?

22
00:01:13,500 --> 00:01:16,310
Pinkie Pie?
I kinda need to get going.

23
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:20,450
Okay. I'm done!

24
00:01:21,520 --> 00:01:24,980
Sooner I get there,
sooner I get to show off my stuff!

25
00:01:25,950 --> 00:01:27,360
See you guys in a week!

26
00:01:27,510 --> 00:01:28,420
Good luck!

27
00:01:28,570 --> 00:01:30,690
Won't need it!

28
00:01:32,360 --> 00:01:36,280
DON'T FORGET TO WRITE!

29
00:01:40,240 --> 00:01:42,600
Do you think she heard me?

